Dear all,
I have ASP.NET Core 2 WebAPI project and I am using successfully logger with Application insights

```
//ILoggerFactory loggerFactory;
ILogger logger = loggerFactory.CreateLogger("MyLog");
loggerFactory.AddApplicationInsights(app.ApplicationServices);
```

I have issues with using LogError and sending custom object that will be forwarded to Application Insights. 

```
decimal myobject = (decimal)3.14;
